# Environment & Scripts

- Node.js v18+ expected. Install deps with `npm install`.
- Environment variables are in `.env.local` (never commit). Copy from `.env.example` and set `DATABASE_URL`.
- Common commands:
  - `npm run dev` for development server
  - `npm run build` for production build
  - `npm run lint` for ESLint
  - `npm run test` for tests (Vitest)
  - Prisma:
    - `npx prisma migrate dev`
    - `npx prisma generate`
    - `npx prisma studio`
    - `npx prisma db push` (avoid in production)

See [README.md](mdc:README.md) for details and context.

